General.Name: Superior Industries International
General.Description: Superior Industries International, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, designs, manufactures, and sells aluminum wheels in North America and Europe. The company offers its products under the ATS, RIAL, ALUTEC, and ANZIO brands. It sells to original equipment manufacturers, aftermarket manufacturers, and suppliers. Superior Industries International, Inc. was founded in 1957 and is headquartered in Southfield, Michigan.
